{"tid":709011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大迫：夢想成真","createTime":"2018-06-19T16:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T06:41:54.000Z","uid":33799,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b006a16405f90b31eac9172937d55faedd36ea","tid":709011,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=f10hdI1SAMbs4T3xEmP7B8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a5319ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】射手大迫勇也周二於世界盃H組為日本奠定勝局，賽後坦言是夢想成真。<br />\n<br />\n日本今戰大部份時間人多打人少，由攻中香川真司先開紀錄，雖然一度被哥倫比亞追成平手，但下半場由效力德甲科隆的大迫勇也（Yuya Osako）接應中場本田圭佑開出的角球頂入，終以2:1勝出。 成為國家英雄的28歲大迫表示：<span style=\"color: red;\">「能夠實現夢想，我真的非常開心。我們賽前很努力練習死球戰術，可以在比賽時運用出來，實在太好了。」</span><br />\n<br />\n至於在上半場射入12碼的多蒙特兵香川真司則表示：「今仗取得勝利後，終於鬆了一口氣。大家都明白首勝的重要性，但現在只是第1場，緊接下來還要為下仗作備戰。」日本下仗在下周日鬥塞內加爾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ee5fd54a24973aba50c914a3a182f4a9fe1c53","tid":709011,"uid":33799,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"日本周二在世界盃擊敗哥倫比亞，日前發生地震的大阪，有市民表示今次勝仗，令他們獲得勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n大阪北部有組織舉辦了睇波party，有超過200名球迷組團一起睇直播。他們看著攻中香川真司、前鋒大迫勇也（Yuya Osako）先後建功，帶領日本國家隊於世界盃H組首輪，以2:1擊敗哥倫比亞，成為世界盃史上首支擊敗南美洲球隊的亞洲球隊。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 完場後，全場球迷都站起來齊聲向著熒光幕說「多謝！」有球迷就表示，香川就大阪地震發表的言論，令人十分感動，亦有人認為，日本今場取勝，令他們獲得到勇氣，在今次地震中堅強。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e78cf44ed7b6dcc5dcb9e2f7fe30f11025b324b","tid":709011,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c474397f97fd1e6606d537e1d78f5b0ee8e7db","tid":709011,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40015942ddef9e405d29b6077c3a4b62ca1acf94","tid":709011,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61d334e8bb40c55ccbc60b6a925f4c3abeb2cf05","tid":709011,"uid":93883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"發表左咩言論？"},{"pid":"839f785b1edfca007a539a2ddfc25c599b69a6f9","tid":709011,"uid":34490,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"40015942ddef9e405d29b6077c3a4b62ca1acf94","tid":709011,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"輸幾多呀傻閪？"},{"pid":"800ffa17200832bdd24f12e2b4810d5e3044482c","tid":709011,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"839f785b1edfca007a539a2ddfc25c599b69a6f9","tid":709011,"uid":34490,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"40015942ddef9e405d29b6077c3a4b62ca1acf94","tid":709011,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"輸幾多呀傻閪？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"唔好再激佢，我驚佢跳樓"},{"pid":"dbbf17cd88daea88d8e65d89279434b5d7f8c81b","tid":709011,"uid":34490,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"800ffa17200832bd